# Cloudflare Pages 边缘响应头配置
# 文档：https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/headers/
# 这是 Pages 默认子域上**唯一**可下发的反爬硬控信号——
# 已绑定自定义域名 lewisdocs.cadapi.dev 后，可叠加 zone 级 WAF 规则
# （见 project-docs/03-development.md §13）。_headers 仍保留作为底线 + 双重保险。

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 全站默认：所有路径都拒索引 + 反 iframe + 反内嵌
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive, nosnippet, noimageindex, nocache
  Referrer-Policy: no-referrer
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
  Permissions-Policy: browsing-topics=(), interest-cohort=()
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 蜜罐：永不缓存，让命中必达 CF Analytics
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/_honeypot/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive
  Cache-Control: no-store, no-cache, must-revalidate
  Pragma: no-cache

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# 政策文件：短缓存（5 分钟），改 robots/ai 后能快速生效
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
/robots.txt
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=300
/ai.txt
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=300
/LICENSE
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=300
